tika.dc.description: Well-dressed women always have a dominant style that both influences all their 'looks' and also reflects their inner personality. Young girls are taught how to use feminine clothing, make-up, hair and accessories to achieve this from an early age. Unfortunately you probably weren't. To help you find your own great look, this short ebook includes a brief overview of our seven 'archetypal' female looks. Our clients always find themselves drawn to one or two of these archetypes more than others, and each forms the foundation of their own individual great look. Are you a glam-puss, sporty, classic, or one of the other types? To help you work it out, part two of this useful little ebook is a questionnaire to get you on the right track.
